cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories as it deals with object detection in autonomous driving scenes. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as it proposes a new loss function for improving the performance of 3D object detection. Additionally, it may belong to the natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category as the paper discusses the use of focal loss in image-based object detection.
